"There were only two of us there.
We were the whole world.
[r]But it's not like that here. There are a lot of people. There are a lot of people other than us. It's easy to contact them. [l][r]
That's what made us drift apart. [l][r]
[r]I feel uncomfortable when you talk to anyone other than me.
…That’s right, I was jealous. [l][r]
[r]For example, if I try to contact someone but don't get a reply, I feel anxious. [r]
Even if you have a way to contact them, if you don't get a reply, it's scary. [l][r]

[_tb_end_text]

